  "decision_conditions": [
    "&lt;p&gt;&lt;span id=&quot;docs-internal-guid-834f6deb-7fff-605a-a34b-5b45af07a630&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:13.999999999999998pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Insufficient information has been provided to demonstrate that the impact of the proposed use on the amenity of residential neighbours will be mitigated. The proposed change of use is therefore considered unacceptable and would result in an overconcentration of night time economy uses in this location to the detriment of the surrounding residential amenity. As such the proposed development is contrary to policies D13 (Agent of Change) and D14 (Noise) the London Plan (2021) and policies LP2 (Development and amenity), LP38 (Evening and Night Time Economy) and LP58 (Improving the Environment - Pollution) of the Hackney Local Plan LP33(2020).&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;",
    "&lt;p&gt;&lt;span id=&quot;docs-internal-guid-7478102a-7fff-4c17-3a70-ccfce52969c2&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:13.999999999999998pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;The proposed loss of employment generating floor space within a Priority Office Area, would result in a detrimental impact to the supply of office floorspace within this designated area and the borough generally. As such, the proposed development is contrary to policies E1 (Offices) and E2 (Providing suitable business space) of the London Plan (2021) and policy LP27 (Protecting and Promoting Office Floorspace in the Borough) of the Hackney Local Plan LP33(2020).&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;"
